      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个展示双向合并流程的Git图。主题是\"Two-way merges\"，布局用从左到右的方式比较直观。先有一个main分支，然后分出develop分支，两边来回merge几次。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title: Two-way merges (left-to-right)",
        "gitGraph LR",
        "main branch",
        "develop branch",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，从左到右布局。我理解为：先在main上commit，然后checkout到develop分支做开发，之后再merge回main。这个develop分支要checkout几次？merge是双向的对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout develop",
        "checkout main",
        "merge develop",
        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，双向的。develop checkout两次，main也checkout两次。具体流程是：main先commit，然后branch出develop，checkout到develop commit一次，回到main merge develop，main再commit一次。然后checkout develop去merge main，develop再commit，最后回到main再merge一次develop。这样形成两次双向merge。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch develop",
        "checkout develop",
        "checkout main",
        "merge develop",
        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把框架搭出来：标题设为\"Two-way merges (left-to-right)\"，方向LR。main分支起始commit，然后branch develop，checkout过去做第一次commit。现在准备回到main做第一次merge。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "LR",
        "main",
        "commit",
        "branch develop",
        "checkout develop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "继续，checkout main之后merge develop，然后main再commit一次。这次commit表示合并后的稳定版本。之后要checkout develop去merge main，让develop也能同步main的最新内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "merge develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout develop",
        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：checkout main后merge develop，然后commit。现在checkout到develop，准备merge main。develop merge main之后还需要再commit一次对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout develop",
        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，develop merge main之后要commit一次，表示develop也更新了。最后checkout main再merge一次develop，完成整个双向merge的循环。这样main和develop都互相merge过两次。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "merge main",
