    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。develop在merge main后commit，最后checkout main merge develop。整个图从左到右展开，两个分支形成交叉的merge关系，清晰展示了双向同步的流程。",
